      <title>ETF 成交量飙升，中国股市午后延续涨势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/chinese-stocks-decline-as-2024-growth-target-fails-to-impress</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一些跟踪中国股市的交易所交易基金成交量激增，这表明在一些投资者对政府的增长目标表示失望后，国家支持的基金正在支撑市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/chinese-stocks-decline-as-2024-growth-target-fails-to-impress</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 01:58:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
